take a bowl and add half table spoon of spice powder and a half pinch of turmeric powder to it
then add 2 pinches of salt and 2 pinches of masala powder to it
take 10 ml of water and pour it in the above bowl and mix well the contents added 
then take a egg, break it and add it to the above mixture
mix well the whole mixture with a spoon
now take a pan and put it on the stove with medium flame
spread half table spoon of oil to the heated pan
now pour the well mixed egg onto the pan spreading it evenly
wait for half a minute before flipping it onto a plate

place some tomato sauce on it if you are a fan of it
yummy half boiled omlette is ready.enjoyy!

